Add @eggs{2} one at a time, reserving 1/2 yolk in a small dish with a few drops of water.

Mix in @almond extract{1 1/2 tsp} and @gluten-free all-purpose flour{3 cups} until combined.

Press the dough into pan.

Spread the reserved yolk mixture evenly on top.

